What We Do

Super Resolution Location Tracking for 5G System

Current Status

Market Opportunity

FCC Order

U.S. Federal Communications Commission (FCC) mandates supporting E911 in all cellphones. 

It requires location accuracy of 911 callers within 3m

(FCC notice, Feb. 2015,

E911 Phase-II requirements)

Duty

Should they fail to provide exact location information, mobile operators may face heavy penalty every year

Opportunity

We can provide patented super accurate 5G positioning technology that can meet 

FCC requirement
